Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:05.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:06.96,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:08.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.19,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If Arata comes to watch us,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:15.32,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to show off my team, \Nand how strong we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.00,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Watch us play, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.82,0:00:25.44,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second round \Nof the group stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:27.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We're up against Yamaguchi \NMioka High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:30.05,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Mioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.40,0:00:31.99,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi Mioka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.52,0:00:34.05,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi Mioka is the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:38.05,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,public school with the most students \Naccepted to Tokyo University!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:41.22,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,The star of public high schools...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.23,0:00:44.08,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,They're all wearing glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:45.83,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Desktomu-kun times five...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:48.69,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:54.19,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He started placing the cards from \Nthe left after shuffling them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:56.49,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,They all used that method?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.51,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no pattern \Nto their placement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:01.53,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,They're that confident in \Ntheir memorization skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:04.55,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not what we \Nshould be worrying about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.43,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,The three guys over there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.99,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,won the All Japan High \NSchool Quiz Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:13.61,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they playing karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.41,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we keep getting matched \Nagainst weird opponents?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:28.70,Chiha-flashback,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,The five of you have to get us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:34.01,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We absolutely have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how \Ndistinguished their school is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:39.27,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if \Nthey're quiz champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.31,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We've spent so much time \Non competitive karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:44.82,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We can do this, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.00,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:02:02.10,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:05.01,Chiha-ep-title-verse,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)}Verse 10
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:05.01,Chiha-ep-title-poem,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,900)}Rain \Ntakes \Nlonger \Nto dry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:07.87,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Naniwa Bay, now the flower \Nblooms, but for winter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:15.93,Chiha-flashback,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,You may be barred from playing \Nin the tournament tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.13,door,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,No unauthorized personnel allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.13,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.22,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's never been an incident \Nwith substituting before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:25.47,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I could ask a friend of \Nmine who coaches baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:29.02,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, baseball is tough on violations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.93,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We should look towards a \Nsport that isn't as harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:35.11,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Letting this slide won't teach \Nour students anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:41.99,committee,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Committee\N Member\N\NMasuoka\NMasato \N(Grade 6)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.80,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,If his purpose here is to participate \Nin the individual tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.99,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,it is our duty as educators to \Npunish him by taking that away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:45.03,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, you must realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:52.62,cant,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,1)}They're close acquaintances
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:52.62,because,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(120,1)}So they can't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:47.54,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Wataya Arata-kun is special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.60,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's the grandson \Nof an Eternal Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:52.62,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.85,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,He's a truly marvelous karuta player.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:04:03.22,hello,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.79,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I dare say that Master Suo can
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.52,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,only be defeated if Wataya-kun \Ncontinues to mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.76,white,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Sunglasses \Naren't \Nallowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:06.13,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I can't deny that Master Suo is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:10.93,white,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,3000)}Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:09.16,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,But his strange behavior \Nmakes it difficult to use
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:10.78,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,him as a role model for children.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:16.79,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I truly believe that it is our duty \Nto nurture Wataya-kun's growth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.97,Chiha-internal,Kuri,0000,0000,0000,,So much pressure on Arata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:22.07,Chiha-internal,Mura,0000,0000,0000,,So much hate for Master Suo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.99,ionno,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,I don't \Nknow if I'll \Ngraduate \Nthis year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:23.99,Chiha-internal,D,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.49,Chiha-internal,D,0000,0000,0000,,Master Suo is the biggest headache \Nthe karuta world has ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:30.14,Chiha-internal,D,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I want to see him \Nlose as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:31.39,ionno,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(1,2000)}I don't know when \NI will graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:32.08,Chiha-internal,D,0000,0000,0000,,but that doesn't make this right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.96,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.92,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't Arata's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.76,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,I asked him to sit down with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.92,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,He helped make this tournament \Nmemorable for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:43.35,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't trying to cheat \Nour way to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:45.43,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted to be able to play a match!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.43,Chiha-overlap,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Shoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:47.49,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Please let Arata play in \Nthe individual tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:48.10,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Shoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:50.69,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!  I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.09,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.76,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.08,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,They can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.53,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I have to accept my punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:04:59.58,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.64,Chiha-main,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:13.90,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm focused on winning the \Nindividual tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.46,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in team tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:17.86,Chiha-flashback,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.21,Chiha-flashback,Sho,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.71,Chiha-flashback,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have started a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.21,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I was just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.34,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Jealous that Taichi and Chihaya \Nhad their own team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:36.27,handwriting,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time, we'll meet in a match.\NArata
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.95,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:39.77,Chiha-internal,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.28,coach,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,250)}Yamaguchi Mioka High School Karuta Advisor\NOikawa Tomonari (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:44.78,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:48.09,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the coach for Yamaguchi \NMioka High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.70,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyauchi, the advisor for Mizusawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.62,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:54.44,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:57.17,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Your members are all third-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.17,0:05:59.10,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,They chose to participate in \Nthis tournament when they're
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.88,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,probably busy studying \Nfor college exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:04.73,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, karuta is very useful in \Nstudying for college exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.13,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:10.23,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,It lets students train their concentration\N and memorization through a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.26,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,A convenient tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.92,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too interested in winning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:18.21,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,but it's funny how we're \Nbeating schools that spend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.39,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,all their time practicing \Ncompetitive karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.15,Chiha-main,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,My, that's terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.86,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Beat the crap out of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.95,spends,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Spends all \Nher time \Npracticing \Nkaruta
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.29,0:06:27.73,Chiha-internal,Miya,0000,0000,0000,,Especially you, Ayase-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.57,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,My life means nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.82,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,The storm will soon carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.06,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:40.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,My style is big on attacking \Nthe opponent's side,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.85,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,but I've never seen cards placed \Nevenly in the middle like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:48.95,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This makes it easier for me to make mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:50.16,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to memorize!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.56,0:06:51.76,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.51,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:00.27,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.77,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He moved all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:09.58,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}so I wish for a memory \Nof you to take with me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.50,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.91,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I focus, I can memorize \Ntheir positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.57,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,None are left...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:13.62,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A dead card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.41,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I moved because he did!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.43,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.55,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that they were
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.18,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,a bunch of intellectuals who \Nwere giving karuta a try,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.01,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,but they understand karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:27.77,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.02,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She typically places "None are"\N towards the upper left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:40.18,committee,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi Mioka High School\NQuiz Society President \Nand Karuta Club Vice-President\NNakayama Manabu (Third-year)\NSpecializes in astronomy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.75,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Such mistakes can arise when you stick
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:36.91,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,to certain placements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:40.18,nickname,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(300,1)}Nicknamed Poseidon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.79,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Karuta is very fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:42.52,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,My first encounter was a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.19,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,When Sasaki from the karuta club \Ncame to see me for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.52,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You want us to practice with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.20,Chiha-flashback,Sasa,0000,0000,0000,,You can draw parallels between \Nbuzzer pressing and karuta,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.99,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,so it might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:57.14,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when I watched the DVD \Nwith the Master and Queen matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.96,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.87,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly like buzzing in \Nearly and the lag effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.50,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Buzzing in early is when:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:12.84,Chiha-flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Question: The Winter Triangle \Nis formed by Procyon, Si—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.52,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,At that point,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.35,Chiha-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,you can guess the rest is "Sirius, and what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.31,Chiha-flashback,All,0000,0000,0000,,Betelgeuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:23.58,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly like unique syllables \Nin competitive karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.71,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The lag effect is when:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.64,Chiha-poem,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,As this trip takes me away...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.94,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren't machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:36.07,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,If I buzz in after hearing "The Winter \NTriangle is formed by Procyon,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:39.41,Chiha-flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,the moderator will still say \Npart of the next word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.15,0:08:43.46,Chiha-flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,The Winter Triangle \Nis formed by Procy—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.26,Chiha-flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,—on, Si—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:45.21,oops,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Oops
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:49.39,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,If I can catch that extra syllable,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:53.03,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I have what they call \N"game sense" in karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.25,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He knew which card to go for after "As"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:58.71,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.22,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.72,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I have to memorize \Ntheir positions again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:05.44,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any game \Nsense to speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.41,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I just have decision-making skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:12.66,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gust of wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.27,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.27,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:17.78,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.29,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Nakayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.50,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm his teacher, and I'd have \Nto describe his intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.92,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and memory as freakish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:37.44,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}hence the name fall leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:34.28,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You have to press the button \Nbefore you can answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:35.67,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.67,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You have to trust in that \Nmoment of inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:39.20,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.94,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, he has guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:47.55,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For you, I head out to the \Nfields to pick spring greens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:43.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A multi-syllable card! Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:49.31,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved that I was \Nable to keep my own card?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:52.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is how I play karuta?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.09,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.86,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,May the time we spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:09:58.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,How many cards did I hit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:10:02.16,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I took a card from the opponent's \Nside, but I was just forcing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.89,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.12,Chiha-overlap,B,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.12,0:10:31.19,Chiha-main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the Queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.34,Chiha-main,D,0000,0000,0000,,So she really did lose weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:40.63,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu-chan's back to the weight \Nshe was at when we played.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:44.68,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Have I grown at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.22,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Shinobu-chan? \NYou're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.06,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the Birdman rally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.07,0:11:01.73,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what?  Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.82,0:11:07.69,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Shinobu-chan, I won't be able to \Nplay in the individual tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:10.11,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,I broke one of the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.36,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.35,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Masuoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:20.70,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,If Wataya Arata isn't playing, I forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.45,Chiha-main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:23.41,Chiha-main,Masu,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking \Nabout, Wakamiya-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.72,Chiha-main,Masu,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen can't drop \Nout of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.33,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you shouldn't joke around...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.37,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:33.23,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,but stop acting cool \Nand lower your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.41,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Beg them to let you play!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.16,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also asking you to let him play.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.39,Chiha-main,Ara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you doing \Nthis, Shinobu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.22,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get to watch the \NBirdman rally, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.66,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you not disappoint me any further?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.57,Chiha-main,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not want to play against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:06.14,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What will Shinobu-chan and \NArata see when they watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.44,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no longer the high \Nschool first-year me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.89,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,No longer the sixth grade me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:15.96,Omi,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Omi Learning Center
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.00,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.42,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely drenched!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.73,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.13,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go watch the match \Nby the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:27.69,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is running around,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.99,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,but that person with glasses \Nis taking it easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.39,0:12:32.63,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.74,Chiha-main,B,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.18,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Hanano-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.06,Chiha-main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,You actually thought to bring an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:38.92,Chiha-main,Hana,0000,0000,0000,,The forecast said the chance of rain was low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:43.59,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the JMA and the websites \NI checked said it would be sunny,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:44.92,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,but the Japan Weather Association
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.63,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,said that there was \Na chance for showers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.62,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:51.74,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,How was the Akashi Girls' match?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.34,0:12:53.75,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the notes I took.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.45,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,How do you think our match went?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:59.15,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of people \Nso it's not easy to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:03.01,pink,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,First Akashi Girls' all look ordinary\NGirl in front (with long hair)\NPink checkered handbag (Ponita)\Nwhite hand towel\Npink macaroon phone strap
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.12,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was too far away to see the cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:06.01,pink,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Girl with glasses \N(ordinary, sharp-tongued, popular)\Nblack handbag with a charm attached\Nwhite plain towel... cell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:06.96,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,but I wouldn't have understood \Nwhat was going on anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:08.80,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Hanano-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.10,cant,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,1)}Even the color \Nof their socks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:10.10,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than enough information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.65,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was so relieved
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.22,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,when you didn't suddenly tell me \Nto play in a match this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:19.10,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,That was a big shock at the Tokyo regional!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:22.44,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Just to be clear, I'm not interested in \Nplaying in the national championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:24.68,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with scouting other teams!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:27.90,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike everyone else, I don't have \Nthe fighting spirit to be a player!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.14,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try to consolidate these notes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:38.10,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,so grab some lunch when \Nyou have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.70,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:48.19,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that everyone else in our \Nclub was itching to play in matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:52.16,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,but Komano-senpai might be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:54.80,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Makes sense to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:58.15,Chiha-internal,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,The world of karuta is too competitive \Nand intense. Who wants that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:03.15,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,This is turning out to be a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:08.72,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,Nakayama, your drive to challenge \Nyourself has always impressed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.99,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,To think that you would \Nwork so hard at karuta
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:14.41,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of doing well \Nin the quiz championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:17.36,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what the \Ncoach is thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.31,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,However, in reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.65,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I work hard at the quiz championship \Nfor the sake of karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.92,coach2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Huh?  Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.73,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I love this atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:28.43,coach2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}He's a freak...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.54,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The tension before a card is read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.93,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So silent, you can hear people breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.01,0:14:44.78,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she has crazy lung capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:48.92,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, you can win \Nif you just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.53,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it rushing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:10.92,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I can see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.52,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She's kinda pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.81,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Star-wise, she's a Vega.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.25,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.85,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind it when she \Nlooks down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.85,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.75,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I'm wasting my brainpower \Non unnecessary thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.23,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,How's everyone else doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.41,Chiha-note2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,In the back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.41,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing the other three \Nexcept the one in the back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.82,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.29,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.20,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why he doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:45.62,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Our Suihoku society teaches \Ndefensive karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.33,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent can change his placement \Naround as much as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:51.86,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to prevent him from taking \Nany of the 25 cards on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.43,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,By making that my priority,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.22,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I'm somehow able to take the \Nopponent's cards, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.22,0:16:01.32,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...wet with dew
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:08.44,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}As friends and strangers come \Nand go from the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:03.89,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,A dead card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:08.17,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,A poem by the blind monk Semimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:09.74,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Check...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:15.54,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,There are six poems by \Nmonks on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:22.31,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My fear is not of being forgotten,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:17.72,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.30,0:16:22.06,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,This poem was written by Ukon about \Nher attachment to a man who left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:26.44,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,There are four poems \Nby women on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.05,Chiha-main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.42,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:32.30,Chiha-internal,A,0000,0000,0000,,I keep shuffling my cards around \Nand it doesn't faze her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.72,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,If he's randomly placing his cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:38.00,Chiha-internal,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,then I won't bother remembering \Nthem by position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.95,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit that it's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.07,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Their style has no fixed card placement
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.33,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,and frequently moves the cards around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.23,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But in karuta, you're only \Nallowed to move your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:52.84,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Against opponents who aren't \Ngreat at memorization,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.40,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,his swing is fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:56.49,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm good at memorization.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.70,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.16,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Their emphasis is on \Nmemorization and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.16,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I play karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:09.32,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You need mental and physical \Nstrength to play karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.17,Chiha-internal,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I only memorize about half the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:15.55,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Nishida was trying to teach me that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.41,0:17:17.65,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,your body is important too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:20.43,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It takes both mind and body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:23.18,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her get into a groove.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:24.97,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.73,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,And heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:30.27,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!  How many times is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:32.18,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!  Can he really memorize them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.99,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Kill!  Kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:33.99,Chiha-overlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.63,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.63,0:17:37.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.03,memorizeL,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Can memorize
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.03,memorizeR,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Can't memorize
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.03,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to the group that \Ncan't memorize too well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:43.88,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Once I realized that, \NI felt a lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:46.21,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,While I sigh and lament...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:46.21,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.99,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When the misty bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:48.62,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:52.23,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've faced \Nsomeone who keeps moving his cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:54.42,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.57,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,If I stick it out long enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:00.64,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,There, they're almost all \None-syllable cards now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.02,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving my cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.12,0:18:05.52,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,He's moving them back now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:12.57,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...that this love has \Nalso sullied my name
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:08.24,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,and he moved them to a strange spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.28,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's go time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:16.32,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,Note that though...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.49,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She moved the instant the reader spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.12,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She moved faster than sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:25.41,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,...I shall return to you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:28.37,Chiha-poem,N,0000,0000,0000,,When I must hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:29.54,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even get a chance to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:32.15,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I trust my inspiration and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.85,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,My inspiration travels \Nthrough my brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.81,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But in her case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:42.99,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It goes straight from \Nher ear to her finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.92,0:18:46.36,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She's no Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.36,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,She's as sharp as...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:52.72,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,...Bellatrix of the constellation Orion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:55.00,Chiha-internal,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,The Amazon Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.86,group,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Yamaguchi Mioka High School \NNakayama Manabu X \NHayashi Sosuke X \NToyota Hiroichi O \NSasaki Makoto X \NTokoro Daisuke O
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:01.04,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya, don't fall asleep \Nwhile standing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:01.36,group,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Mizusawa High School\N Ayase Chihaya O \NMashima Taichi O \NOe Kana X \NNishida Yusei O \NTsukuba Akihiro X
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.30,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.08,Chiha-main-top,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You were so close, Kana-chan!  \NYou lost by two cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:05.39,Chiha-main-top,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I was close, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:06.62,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chihaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:06.98,Chiha-main-top,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,You lost by 12 cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.03,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,You all did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.69,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts to lose in the group stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.63,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,but this experience will \Nhelp in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.37,Chiha-main,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll help in \Nthe Quiz Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.18,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It won't help...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:20.57,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.52,0:19:23.78,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,This loss was a loss in karuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.14,Chiha-main,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll avenge it by playing karuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:34.61,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are so smart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.06,Chiha-internal,Oi,0000,0000,0000,,and so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.80,0:19:43.58,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.59,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on advancing \Nto the playoffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.59,0:19:47.48,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some homemade cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:52.17,cookie,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)}I won't have any
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.14,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,How did the other schools do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.60,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Was it rough moving around \Nin the rain, Komano?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.52,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,It was no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.74,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, speaking of which, the \NQueen was completely drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:58.18,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I saw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:20:01.04,scary,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,It was \Nscary!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:19:59.66,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,She walked in dripping wet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.66,0:20:02.16,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,then she helped this person \Nin a Fukui T-shirt and begged
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:04.95,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,them to let him play in \Nthe individual tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:06.73,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Because she wanted to play him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:09.60,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,So the Queen has a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.54,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.29,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Arata and Shinobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:19.55,Chiha-internal,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Because she wants to play him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.02,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Sumire-chan, can you tell me what—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.89,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time for that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.46,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.59,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come up with the \Norder for our next match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.93,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.04,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Queen and Arata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.24,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Those words will distract Chihaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:39.00,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,I need her to focus \Non the team match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:42.50,Chiha-internal,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,So Arata is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.62,Chiha-internal,,0000,0000,0000,,here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.05,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:48.73,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Komano-senpai should
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.73,0:20:51.02,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,be a starting member for the playoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.18,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.09,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're tired, so you \Nwant to switch out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:54.64,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.22,Chiha-main,Sumi,0000,0000,0000,,So you must not want \Nto play that badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.47,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.69,Chiha-main,Tsu,0000,0000,0000,,Komano-senpai will know better how \Nto use all the data he's collected!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.03,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:05.84,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Either Tsukuba-kun or I can drop out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.91,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Desktomu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:10.91,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...  I'd say...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:12.92,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.65,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should use the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:18.79,Chiha-main,,0000,0000,0000,,same members we've been \Nusing for the next match.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:19.84,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.34,0:21:23.96,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should go without Desktomu-kun.
